# atur_keuangan

Berisi dokumentasi API aplikasi atur_keuangan.

## Users [/api_atur_keuangan/users]

Berisi API terkait dengan tabel users

### Sign in [POST /api_atur_keuangan/users/signin]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "email": "amastini22@gmail.com",
                "password": 1234
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "status": true,
                "token": "e32kugdiu238cf238hc0923j9skmqecjvecyvuew",
                "user": [
                    "id": 1
                ]
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "message": "Error retrieving user email amastini22@gmail.com"
            }
            
