    + id (number) - ID User
    
+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "files":[
                    "photo": {
                        "name": "360px-Cute_Monkey_cropped.jpg",
                        "mimetype": "image/jpeg",
                        "size": 48614
                    },
                ]
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

