## Order [/api_atur_keuangan/orders]

### Create [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            token: <Token anda didapat ketika melakukan sign-in>
    
    + Body
    
            {
                "nama_kegiatan": "Makan Bakso",
                "tanggal: "13-08-2020",
                "harga": 20000,
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1,
                "nama_kegiatan": "Makan Bakso",
                "tanggal: "13-08-2020",
                "harga": 20000,
                "struk": "-", 
                "user_id": 1,
                "updatedAt": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                "createdAt": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
            }
            
